<headline>Special Weather Statement issued November 01 at 1:57PM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Locally Dense Fog in the Helena Valley This Afternoon...
Dense fog in the Helena Valley is decreasing in areal coverage
this afternoon. Locally dense fog across the central and northern
Helena Valley will reduce visibility to around a half mile through
4 PM MDT. Motorists should be prepared for icy elevated surfaces
such as bridges where fog continues to be locally dense.</description>
